termcapinfo xterm*|linux*|rxvt*|Eterm* OP                #Optimize Term status over ASCII
termcapinfo xterm 'is=\E[r\E[m\E[2J\E[H\E[?7h\E[?1;4;6l' #Window resize bugfix


